    "body": "  PhD in quantitative marketing bridging research and practice  I study how firms innovate and make strategic choices. In parallel, I help companies tackle business problems in data-rich settings, using evidence to guide decisions rather than intuition.   Research  Practice  Teaching  Projects  Blog                                      Recent Blog Posts:                                                                                            The Ideal Salesperson              :       The Ideal Salesperson in the Age of Digital Platforms: Consultant, or Facilitator?:                                                                               Rodrigo Farinha                 01 Sep 2025                                                                                                                       Welcome              :       Why I’m Starting This Blog:                                                                               Rodrigo Farinha                 14 May 2025                             "
